# OpenSpec — StormSentinel Specification

## Project Overview

| Field | Value |
|----|----|
| Project Name | Storm Sentinel |
| Platform | Flutter 全平台 (Android, iOS, Web, macOS, Windows, Linux) |
| Language | Dart (SDK >=3.4.0) |
| UI Framework | 评估中 (spike/material3 vs spike/forui) |
| Build System | Flutter CLI + build_runner (代码生成) |
| Architecture | Clean Architecture / MVVM |
| State Management | Riverpod (AsyncNotifier) |
| Networking | Dio |
| Routing | go_router |
| DI | Riverpod (Provider 即 DI 容器) |
| Data Models | freezed + json_serializable |
| Local Storage | shared_preferences |

## Kotlin ↔ Flutter 概念映射

| Kotlin / Compose | Flutter / Riverpod |
|----|----|
| `ViewModel` | `AsyncNotifier` / `Notifier` |
| `StateFlow<UiState>` | `AsyncValue<T>` (Loading/Data/Error) |
| `Repository` interface | `abstract class` + `Provider<Repo>` |
| `@Inject` / Hilt `@Module` | `Provider` / `ref.read()` / `ref.watch()` |
| `Retrofit` + `OkHttp` | `Dio` + `ApiClient` + `Interceptor` |
| `Kotlin data class` | `freezed` class (or plain Dart class) |
| `NavHost` / `NavGraph` | `GoRouter` / `GoRoute` / `ShellRoute` |
| `collectAsState()` | `ref.watch(provider)` |
| `viewModel.doSomething()` | `ref.read(provider.notifier).doSomething()` |
| `SavedStateHandle` | `FamilyAsyncNotifier` + 路由参数 |
| `DataStore` / `SharedPreferences` | `shared_preferences` |
| `Timber` | `logger` |
| `KSP` / `KAPT` | `build_runner` |

## Module Structure

```
lib/
├── core/                  # 纯 Dart 业务层，零 UI 依赖
│   ├── models/            # 数据模型 (WeatherAlert, AlertSeverity, LocationInfo)
│   ├── repositories/      # 仓库抽象接口
│   ├── services/          # 业务逻辑 (AnomalyDetectionService)
│   └── utils/             # 通用工具 (Result<T>)
├── data/                  # 数据层实现
│   ├── api/               # Dio 网络层 (ApiClient, Interceptors, ApiException)
│   ├── mock/              # Mock 数据（原型期）
│   └── repositories/      # 仓库具体实现
├── providers/             # Riverpod DI 容器（对应 Hilt Modules）
│   ├── dio_provider.dart
│   ├── repository_providers.dart
│   └── service_providers.dart
├── router/                # go_router 路由配置（对应 NavGraph）
│   └── app_router.dart
├── features/              # 功能模块（MVVM 单元）
│   ├── alert_list/
│   │   ├── alert_list_page.dart          # View (Widget)
│   │   └── alert_list_view_model.dart    # ViewModel (AsyncNotifier)
│   ├── alert_detail/
│   │   ├── alert_detail_page.dart
│   │   └── alert_detail_view_model.dart
│   └── settings/          # 待实现
├── ui/                    # UI 框架层（按 spike 分支各自实现）
│   └── theme/
└── main.dart              # 入口 + ProviderScope
```

## Branch Strategy

| Branch | Purpose |
|----|----|
| `main` | 稳定发布分支 |
| `develop` | 共享架构层基础 (core + data mock) |
| `feature/framework-foundation` | 框架层 (Riverpod + Dio + go_router) |
| `spike/material3` | Material 3 + flex_color_scheme UI 原型 |
| `spike/forui` | Forui UI 原型 |

## Key Design Decisions

- **core/ 层不允许 import flutter/material.dart**
- **providers/ 层是 DI 的唯一入口** — 不要在 Widget 中直接 new Repository
- **ViewModel 使用 AsyncNotifier** — 自动管理 Loading/Data/Error 三态
- **路由使用 go_router ShellRoute** — 底部导航不重建页面
- **API 错误统一为 ApiException sealed class** — 所有网络错误一处处理

## Naming Conventions

- 文件名：snake_case (`weather_alert.dart`)
- 类名：PascalCase (`WeatherAlert`)
- Provider 名：camelCase + Provider 后缀 (`weatherRepositoryProvider`)
- ViewModel：PascalCase + ViewModel 后缀 (`AlertListViewModel`)
- 路由路径：kebab-case (`/alert/:id`)
